summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 66W, Page 159 of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Tract 8, Sunnyside Five Acre Tracts from Single Family Residence High Density (RS 5000) Zone to Community Business (BC) Zone (Petition of George C. Pallis, C.F. 289272).
